   "source": [
    "#| label: gfc-proxy-chart\n",
    "#| echo: false\n",
    "fig = go.Figure()\n",
    "fig.add_trace(go.Scatter(x=gfc_daily.index, y=gfc_daily[\"Daily proxy\"], mode=\"lines\", name=\"Daily\", line={\"color\": PALETTE[\"blue_deep\"], \"width\": 1.2}, hovertemplate=\"%{x|%d %b %Y}<br>Daily: %{y:.2f}<extra></extra>\"))\n",
    "fig.add_trace(go.Scatter(x=gfc_monthly.index, y=gfc_monthly[\"Monthly proxy\"], mode=\"lines\", name=\"Monthly\", line={\"color\": PALETTE[\"orange\"], \"width\": 2.2}, hovertemplate=\"%{x|%b %Y}<br>Monthly: %{y:.2f}<extra></extra>\"))\n",
    "fig.add_hline(y=0, line_width=1, line_color=\"rgba(29,37,44,0.30)\")\n",
    "fig.update_layout(**base_layout(left=58), yaxis={\"title\": \"Standardized value (cumulative)\", \"showgrid\": False, \"zeroline\": False, \"linecolor\": \"rgba(29,37,44,0.35)\"})\n",
    "fig.show(config={\"displayModeBar\": False, \"responsive\": True})"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0a332eac",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.chart-card}\n",
    "::: {.lang-en}\n",
    "#### Covered Interest Parity deviations in CHF-USD \n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.chart-card-text}\n",
    "Monthly USD-CHF CIP basis using SOFR vs SARON (3m, 6m) and government debt (3m), spot and forward exchange rate rates.\n",
    "\n",
    "$$CIPD_t^{(T)} = \\left(r_{USD,t}^{(T)} - r_{CHF,t}^{(T)}\\right) + \\frac{1}{T}\\log\\left(\\frac{F_t^{(T)}}{S_t}\\right)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "[Repository](https://github.com/iweigandi/usd-chf-cip-deviations)\n",
    ":::\n",
    ":::\n",
    "::: {.lang-es}\n",
    "#### Desviaciones de la Paridad de Tasas de Interés Cubierta en CHF-USD \n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.chart-card-text}\n",
    "Bases mensuales de CIP USD-CHF utilizando SOFR vs SARON (3m, 6m) y deuda gubernamental (3m), y tipos de cambio spot y forward.\n",
    "\n",
    "$$CIPD_t^{(T)} = \\left(r_{USD,t}^{(T)} - r_{CHF,t}^{(T)}\\right) + \\frac{1}{T}\\log\\left(\\frac{F_t^{(T)}}{S_t}\\right)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "[Repositorio](https://github.com/iweigandi/usd-chf-cip-deviations)\n",
    ":::\n",
    ":::"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
