   "source": [
    "#| label: cip-chart\n",
    "#| echo: false\n",
    "fig = go.Figure()\n",
    "cip_series = [\n",
    "    (\"cip_basis_sofr_saron_3m_bps\", \"SOFR-SARON 3m\", PALETTE[\"blue_deep\"]),\n",
    "    (\"cip_basis_sofr_saron_6m_bps\", \"SOFR-SARON 6m\", PALETTE[\"orange\"]),\n",
    "    (\"cip_basis_libor_3m_bps\", \"LIBOR 3m\", PALETTE[\"blue\"]),\n",
    "    (\"cip_basis_government_3m_bps\", \"Government 3m\", PALETTE[\"teal\"]),\n",
    "]\n",
    "for col, name, color in cip_series:\n",
    "    fig.add_trace(go.Scatter(x=cip[\"Date\"], y=cip[col], mode=\"lines\", name=name, line={\"color\": color, \"width\": 1.55}, hovertemplate=f\"%{{x|%b %Y}}<br>{name}: %{{y:.1f}} bps<extra></extra>\"))\n",
    "fig.add_hline(y=0, line_width=1, line_color=\"rgba(29,37,44,0.30)\")\n",
    "fig.update_layout(**base_layout(left=48), yaxis={\"title\": \"Basis points\", \"showgrid\": False, \"zeroline\": False, \"linecolor\": \"rgba(29,37,44,0.35)\"})\n",
    "fig.show(config={\"displayModeBar\": False, \"responsive\": True})"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4cc99bdd",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.chart-card}\n",
    "::: {.lang-en}\n",
    "#### G-SIBs' market leverage\n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.chart-card-text}\n",
    "Market leverage is decomposed into common-factor and idiosyncratic equity-price components for global systemically important banks.\n",
    "\n",
    "$$L_t =  \\sum_b s_b(\\lambda_b\\underbrace{\\eta_t}_{Common} + \\underbrace{u_{b,t}}_{Idiosyncratic}) $$\n",
    "\n",
    "[Repository](https://github.com/iweigandi/gsib-leverage)\n",
    ":::\n",
    ":::\n",
    "::: {.lang-es}\n",
    "#### Apalancamiento de mercado de los G-SIBs\n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.chart-card-text}\n",
    "El apalancamiento de mercado se descompone en factores comunes e idiosincráticos de precios de acciones para los bancos de importancia sistémica global.\n",
    "\n",
    "$$L_t =  \\sum_b s_b(\\lambda_b\\underbrace{\\eta_t}_{Común} + \\underbrace{u_{b,t}}_{Idiosincrático}) $$\n",
    "\n",
    "[Repositorio](https://github.com/iweigandi/gsib-leverage)\n",
    ":::\n",
    ":::"
   ]
  },
